
Execution steps:

 - start stores / workers (any order is fine):
   - alice
   - bob
   - friendmap
   - mapserv
   - snapp

 - publish application code
   - snapp
        snapp_1.0_codebase
        snapp_2.0_codebase linked against snapp_1.0_codebase
   - mapserv
        mapserv_1.0_codebase
   - friendmap
        friendmap_1.0_codebase linked against mapserv_1.0_codebase, snapp_1.0_codebase
        friendmap_2.0_codebase linked against mapserv_1.0_codebase, snapp_1.0_codebase, snapp_2.0_codebase
   - scripts
        fabric/scripts/foo published to foo
        linking against snapp, mapserv, friendmap

 - initialize objects
   - Init@snapp:
        create snapp
   - Init@mapserv:
        create mapserv
   - Init@friendmap <mapserv_uri>:
        create friendmap
        friendmap.service -> mapserv
   - Init@alice <snapp_uri> <mapserv_uri>:
        create alice on snapp,
        add mapserv to alice.locationInfo
   - Init@bob <snapp_uri> <mapserv_uri>
        create bob on snapp
        add bob.friends to bob.locationInfo
        add mapserv to bob.locationInfo
   - AddFriends@alice <bob_uri>:
        add bob to alice.friends
   - AddFriends@bob <alice_uri>:
        add alice to bob.friends

 - run example
   - RunApp@alice:
        invoke friendmap application
        expected output: 10x10 map with bob's location on it.


